.Dd $Mdocdate$
.Dt KSQL_STMT_RESET 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm ksql_stmt_reset
.Nd resets (unbinds) a statement on a database connection
.Sh LIBRARY
.Lb ksql
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.In stdint.h
.In ksql.h
.Ft "enum ksqlc"
.Fo ksql_stmt_reset
.Fa "struct ksql_stmt *stmt"
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Nm
function resets a statement allocated with
.Xr ksql_stmt_alloc 3 ,
effectively just
.Xr sqlite3_reset .
